claim.claim-text:
A flexible display device, comprising:
a first body (210);
a flexible display (300) comprising a first region (310) forming a front surface of the flexible display device, a first connected region (321) extending from the first region (310), and a second connected region (322) extending from the first connected region (321), wherein the first region (310) is coupled to the first body (210);
a second body (220) configured to slide between a first position and a second position relative to the first body (210) and comprising a support (230);
a first cover (215) coupled to the first body (210) to form a rear surface of the flexible display device; and
a second cover (225) coupled to the second body (220) and located underneath the first cover (215) when the second body (220) is at the first position,
wherein when the second body (220) is at the first position, the first connected region (321) is curved around the support (230), and the second connected region (322) is located underneath the first cover (215) and the second cover (225), and
wherein when the second body (220) is at the second position, the first connected region (321) is co-planar with the first region (310), a portion of the second connected region (322) is curved around the support (230), and the second cover (225) is partially overlapped by the first cover (215).
